            <title>[LU-13971] Report Pool Quotas for a user</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13971</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Users will need reports on their Pool Quota usage. The main case being a user received EDQUOT and doesn&apos;t know why. The user will want to know how much quota they&apos;ve used including all OST Pools. If there is no per-pool information than the user will be left guessing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
